node.text:
Taking over Frankie’s account as a part of #TransTakeOver, founded by @ashleemariepreston! 

Tiiiiny bit about me:
I am an artist who identifies Deaf, trans, Jewish, and Chinese. My background includes launching a clothing line with Opening Ceremony, writing as a columnist for Condé Naste’s first queer publication - @Them, and being casted as a queer superhero within Warner Brother’s DC Universe, Titans.

Giving this talk two years ago felt as if I was opening up my diary and reading it to a crowd. It pinpoints three revelations I reached at the beginning of my gender journey.

I would love to know what you think about it!

ps: I answer your most curious questions on Frankie’s Instagram story today ;) #TransgenderAwarenessWeek

node.text: I don’t truly have words to express how much this woman means to me. She has shown me nothing but unconditional love my entire life and in return I have loved her with all my heart.
